        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To change the date for regularly scheduled general elections for Federal office to the first Saturday and Sunday after the first Friday in November in every even-numbered year.</title>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in House</billTextVersionName>
